    "Id": "chassisdef_barghest_BGS-P",
    "Name": "Barghest",
    "Details": "Someone stole this Barghest from the Blakists, and it's taken a good beating since then, Boss. Almost every scrap of the internals have been replaced, and they've managed to stuff some weird-looking pulse lasers into the Legs. This Periphery \"Shotgun\" takes the cake, though. It has internal ammo, looks like someone tried to build an LBX out of duct tape. The entire Cockpit has been re-engineered, complete with a distille and one of those music boxes they have in some older bars. The distille is somehow routed through the Coolshot, it makes some kind of Schnapps.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Cooling Jacket - Laser</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>",
